WEBVTT

00:00.500 --> 00:11.500
Creating your RestoreAssist account takes under two minutes. Click Get Started on the homepage.

00:12.000 --> 00:23.500
Enter your name and email, and create a secure password.

00:24.000 --> 00:35.500
Check your inbox for a verification link and confirm your email.

00:36.000 --> 00:47.500
Add your company name and your A B N.

00:48.000 --> 00:59.500
Then click Activate — your account is live and ready to use.
